'''Sudan''' madɔnnen '''Sudan ka Fasojamana''' ye [[Afrika]] ani [[Arabula]] bɛɛ labɔnba ye fɛnsɛn ta fanfɛ a bɛ jɔyɔrɔ tanan na Dunia jamana fɛnsɛn baw la. A bɛ danbɔ ni [[Misra]] ye saheli fɛ, [[Kɔgɔji Blen]] saheli-kɔrɔn fɛ, [[Eritera]] ani [[Etiopia]] kɔrɔn fɛ, [[Kenya]] ani [[Uganda]] worodugukɔrɔn fɛ, [[Kongo ka Bɛjɛfanga Fasojamana]] ani [[Cɛma Afrika Fasojamana]] worodugutlebi fɛ, [[Cad]] tlebi fɛ, ani [[Libya]] sahelitlebi. Dugu tɔgɔ bɔra Arabukan Bilad-al-sudan la, sɛbɛnni na “Finmanw ka dugu”. Sudan ye sisan jɛn bɛɛla benbaliya kɛlɛ dagayɔrɔ ye ''Failed States Index'' ka jatemina la min ju ye Sɔrasi Fanga ye ani Darfur mankan. O bɛɛ nata, Sudan bɛ jate jamana woro sɔrɔ jidi telinw na dunia kɔnɔ. A faaba ye [[Kartum]] ye.

